## Style Rules

**Sentences:**
- Maximum sentence length: [e.g. 25 words]
- Preferred paragraph length: [e.g. 2-4 sentences]
- Use active voice: [e.g. "The system detects the error" not "The error is detected by the system"]

**Numbers and data:**
- [e.g. Always use digits, not words: "3 weeks" not "three weeks"]
- [e.g. Round to one decimal place maximum]

**Formatting:**
- [e.g. Use bullet lists instead of long inline enumerations]
- [e.g. Bold key terms on first use]
- [e.g. Use tables instead of in-text comparisons]

## Banned Words and Phrases

Words and phrases we NEVER use:
- "Comprehensive"
- "Holistic approach"
- "In today's world"
- "It's worth noting that"
- "This is extremely important"
- "Innovative" (unless literally describing a patent or first-of-its-kind)
- "Leverage" (as a verb)
- "Game-changer"
- "Landscape"
- "Elevate"
- [add your own]

